Automacao 

> criar Media Type
> type: script 
> nome do script (scriptZabbix)
> adicona 3 parametros: 
    - {ALERT,SENDTO} -> para quem eu vou enviar o alerta 
    - {ALERT,SUBJECT}
    - {ALERT,MESSAGE} -> mensagem enviada 

> Operation Zabbix script: 
Problem started at {EVENT.TIME} on {EVENT.DATE}
Problem name: {EVENT.NAME}
Host: {HOST.NAME}
Severity: {EVENT.SEVERITY}

Original problem ID: {EVENT.ID}
{TRIGGER.URL}

